    "speaker": "interviewee",
    "tag": "PF",
    "text": "This is the tombstone where my-- when after my husband was killed. The villager of this little village called, [NON-ENGLISH], made a casket and buried him the night-- the night after it happened-- to the cross-- because they didn't know who he was-- and a French flag. And it-- he was buried there for a-- a few weeks, and then taken out and buried in Paris-- Paris-- Paris.",
